title: Bucks vs. Lakers, Cowboys Must Win This Weekend and Colin's Blazing 5.
itunes:title: Bucks vs. Lakers, Cowboys Must Win This Weekend and Colin's Blazing 5.
description:
Colin explains why the Bucks beating the Lakers is pointless, why the Cowboys must win this weekend, how the Patriots are better than anyone is giving them credit for and his Blazing 5 picks.

Guests include Albert Breer, Eric Dickerson, Joel Klatt, and Jason McIntyre.
